        "timestamp": "2017-12-07 05:12:39.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\n(4 comments)\n\nHi Ravi, just a few questions to determine impact with the merge:\n\n1. do the changes have been tested?\n\n2. there are a few references to ecomp that should be changed to onap.  I'm not sure if it is console code or provided by portal team.\n\n3. are there any companion changes in the packages directory for installation?\n\n4. are there any companion changes needed in the docker project for proper configuration?\n\n5. I think most of the source code is coming from portal team.   Any plans in the near future to reuse binaries provided by portal instead of having a copy of the source code here?\n\nThank you.",
        "patchset_number": 4
      },
